asuran ( english : demon ) is a 1995 tamil language science fiction horror film cinematography and directed by velu prabhakaran and written and produced by r. k. selvamani .   the film features arun pandian and roja in lead roles whilst radharavi , napoleon and senthil play supporting roles .   the film became a failure at box office .   mansoor ali khan reprised his role of veerabhadran from captain prabhakaran .   after half of this film is the remake of the hollywood film predator .   arnold schwarzenegger acted in the film and released in the year 1987 .